release_note: More congratulations and emoji added to the custom card
More congratulations and motivational reminders added
Now when you travel to different countries and change time zones data about completed habits will not be lost
We fixed the correct behavior of swiping back fixed bugs in the animation when highlighting a habit and corrected the display of days in the calendar on the habit detailed page
Added congratulations on completing habits. Now you have more motivation and fewer reasons to skip
We have accelerated the calculation of statistics. The application now works much faster and calculates records in habits in a fraction of a second

Introducing a new feature: repetitive habits and multiple memories. Now you can set a daily goal for a habit such as how many cups of water to drink how many meals to eat or how many pages to read. And choose as many reminders for a habit as you need.
Now you can create non daily habits
Now you can motivate your habit
